+        // ---- Circuit 38: COMPARATOR reads a LECTERN page progress ----
+        // A lectern holding a 5-page book at page index 2 -> getRedstoneSignal = floor(2/4*14)+1 = 8.
+        // The compiled comparator reads vanilla's getAnalogOutputSignal (the live lectern BE) and
